title: Hi, OiOi Fams!!!! Welcome to Na Now News!
description: This is where we share whatever we have done. It can be crazy nothing or ordinary something. There are a lot of them. Let's dig in! Let's build a fun, healthy, and mutually supportive family. Let’s have fun, grow, and thrive together with us! Remember to always embrace all sides of yourself!

body.raw:
# Hi, OiOi Fams!!!!

Welcome to [**BANANOW.LAND**](https://www.bananow.land/ "BANANOW.LAND Official Website")!

**BANANOW.LAND**‘s vision is to build a fun, healthy, and mutually supportive family. With a creative industry background, the founders support this family in promoting, self-branding, and creating.

## Hi, OiOi Fams!!!!

Supported by **Web3** developers and marketing, we also aim to develop the utilization of blockchain technology in a fun way and become a friendly bridge for people outside the **Web3** ecosystem to take advantage of blockchain technology. Just like a **Bananas**!

### Hi, OiOi Fams!!!!

For that purpose, **BANANOW.LAND** creates the **BANANOW NFTs** collection as the first brand product with many usabilities for the holders. **BANANOW NFTs** are also the main **BANANOW Tokens** that are used as entry-pass to access all privileges in the **BANANOW.LAND**.

#### Hi, OiOi Fams!!!!

But first of all, since there are some who will try to take advantage of you from us, we strongly recommend to read this list of **BANANOW.LAND** official links:

- **BANANOW.LAND** Website: [www.bananow.land](https://www.bananow.land/ "BANANOW.LAND Official Website")
- **BANANOW.LAND** Green Print: [gp.bananow.land](https://gp.bananow.land/ "BANANOW.LAND White Paper")
- **BANANOW.LAND** News: [news.bananow.land](https://news.bananow.land/ "Na Now News Community Media")
- **BANANOW NFTs** Minting Page: [heads.bananow.land](https://heads.bananow.land/ "Official Minting Page of BANANOW NFTs")
- **BANANOW NFTs** on Basescan: [bananow.land/basescan](https://www.bananow.land/basescan/ "BANANOW BASED NFTs Smart Contract")
- **BANANOW NFTs** on OpenSea: [bananow.land/base](https://www.bananow.land/base "BANANOW BASED NFTs on OpenSeo.IO")
- **BANANOW.LAND** Discord: [bananow.land/discord](https://www.bananow.land/discord/ "BANANOW.LAND Discord Server")
- **BANANOW.LAND** X – Twitter: [bananow.land/twitter](https://www.bananow.land/twitter/ "BANANOW.LAND Account on X - Twitter")
- **BANANOW.LAND** Instagram: [bananow.land/instagram](https://www.bananow.land/instagram/ "BANANOW.LAND Account on Instagram")
- **BANANOW.LAND** YouTube: [bananow.land/youtube](https://www.bananow.land/youtube/ "BANANOW.LAND YouTube Channel")

##### Hi, OiOi Fams!!!!

Please view and access the important links above for details and updates. Always double-check for any link you try to access.

> One thing to remember! We will never do a surprise drop or a limited sale. You will be informed days in advance when it happens.

Always check the announcement in our Discord server!

## Come to Our Land!!!!

Besides **BANANOW NFTs**, there are additional **BANANOW Tokens** that are all NFTs and FTs that are accepted in **BANANOW.LAND** to grant roles and access all channels in our Discord server.

[![](/images/posts/welcome-to-na-now-news-1.jpg)](/images/posts/welcome-to-na-now-news-1.jpg)

### Come to Our Land!!!!

Below is the complete list of all additional **BANANOW Tokens** on the markets:

1. **Lord of BANANOW** Collection on Ethereum: [bananow.land/lord](https://www.bananow.land/lord/ "Lord of BANANOW on OpenSea.IO")
2. **BANANOW Tree** Collection on Ethereum: [bananow.land/tree](https://www.bananow.land/tree/ "BANANOW Tree on OpenSea.IO")
3. **Deprecated BANANOW NFTs** Collection on Ethereum: [bananow.land/opensea](https://www.bananow.land/opensea/ "Deprecated BANANOW NFTs on OpenSea.IO")
4. **LadyME NFTs** Collection on Tezos: [bananow.land/ladyme](https://www.bananow.land/ladyme/ "LadyME NFTs on OBJKT.Com")
5. **The ROTY BROI NFTs** Collection on Polygon: [bananow.land/rotybroi](https://www.bananow.land/rotybroi/ "The ROTY BROI NFTs on OpenSea.IO")
6. **Born2Burn NFTs** Collection. on Tezos: [bananow.land/born2burn](https://www.bananow.land/born2burn/ "Born2Burn NFTs on OBJKT.Com")
7. **Escapeace NOWART 1o1 NFTs** Collection on Ethereum: [bananow.land/escapeace](https://www.bananow.land/escapeace/ "Escapeace NOWART 1o1 NFTs on MarketPlace")

#### Come to Our Land!!!!

Please view and access all the collection links above for collecting. Once again, always double-check for any link you try to access.

##### Come to Our Land!!!!

Let’s have fun, grow, and thrive together with us!  
Remember to always embrace all sides of yourself!

###### Come to Our Land!!!!
